"            <li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" "
"data-caption=\"Il ballo di Drupal\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;blockquote data-caption=\"Dries Buytaert\"&gt;Drupal è "
"fantastico!&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;code data-caption=\"Ciao mondo in "
